File - Preferences - Workspace Settings ou User Settings

* Exemplo
    {
    "files.exclude": {
        "**/.git": true,
        "**/.svn": true,
        "**/.hg": true,
        "**/.DS_Store": true,
        "**/*.js":{
            "when": "$(basename).ts"
        },
        "**/*.js.map": true
    }
}